<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سنة اثنين <span class="c2">(٤)</span> وخمس ماية<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>سُلّمت الموصل لمودود <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
